snippet.title: Longplay of Transformers: Beast Wars Transmetals
snippet.description:
Longplay of Transformers: Beast Wars Transmetals, played as the NTSC version on the Nintendo 64. This game's version was released on Nov. 15th, 2000. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:19 - Opening

Optimus Primal playthrough
02:31 - Metal Warriors Reborn! (vs. Rattrap)
03:30 - Battle in the Wastelands (vs. Tarantulas)
04:32 - Decisive Battle in the Sky (vs. Airazor)
05:49 - Energon Island (vs. Terrorsaur)
07:05 - Giant Cave of Darkness (vs. Cheetor)
08:14 - Breaking Through the Line of Defense (vs. Waspinator)
09:44 - The Mysterious Ancient Ruins (vs. Megatron)
11:02 - Arise, Megatron X (vs. Megatron X)
14:56 - Ending
15:28 - Cast & credits

Endings
18:25 - Rattrap
18:55 - Cheetor
19:22 - Airazor
19:53 - Megatron
20:37 - Tarantulas
21:10 - Waspinator
21:41 - Terrorsaur
22:14 - Tigatron
22:43 - Ravage
23:24 - Blackarachnia
24:00 - Starscream
24:40 - Megatron X
